Change TESTS_ENVIRONMENT to allow running outside build dir.

Signed-off-by: Mihaela Sendrea <mihaela.sendrea@enea.com>
Upstream-status: Pending

Index: libvirt-1.2.4/tests/Makefile.am
===================================================================
